data.description: Tranquility awaits you in this 3 bd, 1 & 3/4 bath open concept Sierra Montana home!  Some upgrades include newer wood blinds throughout, massive ceiling fan in great room, and stylish light fixture in the dining area.  ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED! Some furnishings may be negotiated. See LA for a complete list.  Master ensuite also boasts a walk-in closet.  Enjoy a bbq with friends and family out in the spacious backyard.  Get your creative juices flowing on how to maximize the use of the large concrete pad. Where there are lemons, make lemonade!...or orange juice with the two fruit-bearing trees out back!  Have large toys? They will fit with ease through the double side gate. The east side of home could be a perfect dog run!  Enjoy a stroll w/ the kiddos to the community park or walking paths
